 */

 */

/**
 * Returns info about the current client, including account info, notifications, and WB network status.
 *
 * @param steamTicket - The Steam encrypted application ticket of the account, converted to hex.
 *

 *
 * @example
 *
 * client.info();
 */
members.name: info

members.docComment:
/**
 * Creates an access token, allowing you to access the MultiVersus API.
 *
 * @param username - Username of the account to log in with
 *
 * @param password - Password of the account to log in with
 *
 * @returns {Promise<any>}
 *
 * @example
 *
 * client.login('username', 'password');
 */
members.name: login

members.docComment:
/**
 * Searches for users from a username.

 * @param limit - Limit of users to return.
 *

 *

 *
 * client.searchByUsername('ElijahPepe', 10);
 */
members.name: searchByUsername
